name: Weekday Portraiture Session
description:
Kids (2-12), Teens, Adults (up to 3 people) $25 Additional person.

This will cover the photographers talent and time before, during and after the session. 1.5-2hrs on location shoot with fun and unique spots. A private gallery up to 35 images from your session for viewing only w/25 custom digital negatives w/print release along with 10 digi-pics for facebook and email sharing only. You will also receive a Timeline Cover customized with your images and my logo. 

We will set up a brief coffee or lunch date to get to know each other a little better before the session and talk wardrobe/expectations. 

I look forward to having a blast with you. If you wish to pay in GBP then please contact me and we can go from there. 

*Additional large prints/albums available for purchase see website for pricing www.bleulips.com*

name: London Live Session
description:
It's back! Ever wanted to spend the day in London just to have your pictures taken at various stops, alley ways, landmarks, markets and whatever else you can get yourself into? 

Well I love destination sessions. You will receive:

Password protected online gallery for viewing and selecting only. 
2.5-3 hour session 
1 8x8 custom album
10 5x7 prints on matboard
50 Custom Digital Negatives printable up to 11x14 only w/print release of your selected images.
Blog post of your day w/outtakes
